{
  "texts": [
    "But it is hand-coded, which could lead to coding errors and subjective decisions, and is only available for 5% of cases.",
    "In addition, it could be that the use of economic reasoning in an opinion might be coded as conservative, notwithstanding the associated decision.",
    "Therefore we complement this measure with a machine-coded measure from the available metadata in each case.",
    "In particular, we look at regulatory cases where the government is a party to the case.",
    "We look, in particular, for labor agencies and environmental agencies."
  ]
}